ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What types of blockchain data can this app analyze?

ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How up-to-date is the blockchain information provided by the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app provides near real-time analysis of blockchain data, with updates typically occurring within minutes of new blockchain activity. This ensures you always have access to the most current information for your analysis needs.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I customize the analysis parameters in the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, our app offers extensive customization options. You can set specific parameters, choose particular blockchain networks, filter data by various criteria, and create custom dashboards to suit your unique analysis requirements.
